{"id":584445,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/05/文三娃：在潘董带领下的自媒体大v们/","date":"2018-05-11T05:48:59Z","modified":"2018-05-11T05:48:59Z","title":"文三娃：在潘董带领下的自媒体大V们","content":"<p><em>作者：<a href=\"http://shop.m.taobao.com/shop/shop_index.htm?ut_sk=1.WD2DJhmNFOMDAIRxfbB077%2BF_21380790_1521115880382.Copy.53&amp;shop_navi=allitems&amp;user_id=142079964\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">文涛</a></em></p>\n<p>​​​<b>在潘刚董事长的带领下，国乳伊利有偿站台方阵中的自媒体大V们正微笑着向广大爱国消费者款款走来。 </b></p>\n<p><b>分列式开始！</b></p>\n<p><b>走在队伍最前面的是观众非常熟悉的孔庆东和点子正。</b></p>\n<p><b>现在步入会场的分别是侯宁、袁国宝、石述思、喻国明、王冲、传媒老王…… </b></p>\n<p><b>等等！鲍迪克老师姗姗来迟，正在检录处签到。</b></p>\n<p>​以上是2018年伊利乳业公关战争中比较具有观赏性的的一次战役素描。</p>\n<p>​自媒体红人的V力，确是赤裸裸的商业价值，乌泱乌泱的网红们，争先恐后要将它变现。</p>\n<p>点子正、孔庆东、侯宁、袁国宝等这些个所谓一到热点事件就为企业或政府站台的舆情专家，还真没辜负了这个时代，吃香喝辣，生冷不忌，追腥逐臭，口味是越来越宽广了 。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXgy1fqzpwjwf1ej30xc18ge0q.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-584448\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXgy1fqzpwjwf1ej30xc18ge0q.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"575\" height=\"767\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXgy1fqzpwjwf1ej30xc18ge0q.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXgy1fqzpwjwf1ej30xc18ge0q-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 575px) 100vw, 575px\" /></a></p>\n<p>如此肆无忌惮，<b> #在潘刚董事长的带领下#</b></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_584465\" style=\"width: 410px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly4fr0pihu4u1j30kj0rdmye.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-584465\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly4fr0pihu4u1j30kj0rdmye.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"533\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly4fr0pihu4u1j30kj0rdmye.jpg 739w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly4fr0pihu4u1j30kj0rdmye-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">大师兄漫画</span></p></div>\n<p>​笔者认为，参与大约8点20分发这样的闭眼型商业群体事件，拿粉丝信任换取个人利益，不是小节有亏，而是既不尊重自己更不尊重公众，大不堪。</p>\n<p><b>点子正</b>老师的名言是“只站对不站队”。</p>\n<p>但这仅仅是一句漂亮话。</p>\n<p>在站台台友里，就有点子正点爷矫健的身影，大约8点20分。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_584467\" style=\"width: 460px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly4fr0pijq8oyj30kj0fsjvf.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-584467\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly4fr0pijq8oyj30kj0fsjvf.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"346\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly4fr0pijq8oyj30kj0fsjvf.jpg 739w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly4fr0pijq8oyj30kj0fsjvf-300x231.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">点子正为国乳站台</span></p></div>\n<p>还以反击境外敌对势力，捍卫国乳的崇高名义，比如北大庆东。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXgy1fqzpwd3svfj30rs1a4n7y.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-584447\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXgy1fqzpwd3svfj30rs1a4n7y.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"747\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXgy1fqzpwd3svfj30rs1a4n7y.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXgy1fqzpwd3svfj30rs1a4n7y-181x300.jpg 181w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXgy1fqzpwd3svfj30rs1a4n7y-617x1024.jpg 617w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>指教北大二十年的庆东教授，可以说是栉风沐雨筚路褴褛，袒胸露背赤膊上阵了。</p>\n<p>为弘扬光大中华乳家文化。 ​​​​</p>\n<p>西元2017年9月30日，孔在流连罗密欧与朱丽叶故居时制造的“摸奶门”，在中外文化交流史上，留下了浓墨重彩的一个爪印。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXgy1fr5hkceynfj30j60xywjw.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-584452\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXgy1fr5hkceynfj30j60xywjw.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"708\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXgy1fr5hkceynfj30j60xywjw.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXgy1fr5hkceynfj30j60xywjw-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXgy1fr5hkceynfj30j60xywjw-578x1024.jpg 578w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<p>​拿另一位网红染香（袁小靓）打艳镲，也是庆东教授乐此不疲的小把戏。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/006Z3tIBgy1flx057w9tnj30hs0n4djr.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-584446\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/006Z3tIBgy1flx057w9tnj30hs0n4djr.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"520\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/006Z3tIBgy1flx057w9tnj30hs0n4djr.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/006Z3tIBgy1flx057w9tnj30hs0n4djr-231x300.jpg 231w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a><br />\n​<br />\n同为挺伊人士和职业站台家，也就<b>鲍迪克</b>老师的表现相对清新脱俗，对通稿做了技术加工，规避了“8点20分发”这样的粗放风格，可以说商业站台界的良心了。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_584470\" style=\"width: 460px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly4fr0piuus5hj30kj0p9qai.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-584470\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly4fr0piuus5hj30kj0p9qai.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"554\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly4fr0piuus5hj30kj0p9qai.jpg 739w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly4fr0piuus5hj30kj0p9qai-244x300.jpg 244w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">鲍迪克挺伊</span></p></div>\n<p>而像<b>王冲</b>先生这样的道歉并自罚，已属罕见，大多数参与者的人设里，根本就没有这个选项。 ​​​​</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_584469\" style=\"width: 460px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly4fr0pins6r4j30kj0pyafs.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-584469\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly4fr0pins6r4j30kj0pyafs.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"569\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly4fr0pins6r4j30kj0pyafs.jpg 739w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly4fr0pins6r4j30kj0pyafs-237x300.jpg 237w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">王冲就伊利问题道歉</span></p></div>\n<p>这会儿的点爷，开始为自己的商业站队提出了理直气壮的解释。更是公开邀约营销公司继续私信勾搭。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_584468\" style=\"width: 460px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly4fr0pijr2rnj30kj0oyn78.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-584468\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly4fr0pijr2rnj30kj0oyn78.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"547\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly4fr0pijr2rnj30kj0oyn78.jpg 739w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly4fr0pijr2rnj30kj0oyn78-247x300.jpg 247w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">没有公开私信的习惯</span></p></div>\n<p>互联网是有记忆的，但有些知名互联网友是会选择性遗忘的。</p>\n<p>咳咳，咳咳。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_584466\" style=\"width: 460px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly4fr0pijjo5pj30kj0utgsf.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-584466\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly4fr0pijjo5pj30kj0utgsf.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"675\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly4fr0pijjo5pj30kj0utgsf.jpg 739w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly4fr0pijjo5pj30kj0utgsf-200x300.jpg 200w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly4fr0pijjo5pj30kj0utgsf-682x1024.jpg 682w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">晒私信</span></p></div>\n<p>点爷名言：只站对不站队。</p>\n<p>​而政治站队和商业站台恰恰是他的双热爱。</p>\n<p>点爷见天儿就赌咒发誓拼人品，高喊拿钱发帖死全家，木有小JJ。</p>\n<p>但我觉得，这誓发得……</p>\n<p>虎毒还不食子呢，况名人乎？</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_584449\" style=\"width: 460px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXgy1fr0pdw8ueoj30rs19w7kl.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-584449\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXgy1fr0pdw8ueoj30rs19w7kl.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"743\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXgy1fr0pdw8ueoj30rs19w7kl.jpg 1000w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXgy1fr0pdw8ueoj30rs19w7kl-182x300.jpg 182w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXgy1fr0pdw8ueoj30rs19w7kl-768x1269.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXgy1fr0pdw8ueoj30rs19w7kl-620x1024.jpg 620w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">收钱发帖死全家</span></p></div>\n<p>​自媒体大V集体有偿站台事故后，王冲先生头一个儿痛快道歉并自罚。</p>\n<p>有推友评：伊利脱掉了很多人的底裤，像王冲这样勇于穿起来的，凤毛麟角。</p>\n<p>不过名犯冲字啊，认怂的大V还是大V麽？</p>\n<p>您看石述思和袁国宝两位先生多老道，慎一慎，新华社的援兵就到了。</p>\n<p>​<br />\n<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr32ma25ffj30rs1jvdy2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-584461\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr32ma25ffj30rs1jvdy2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"905\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr32ma25ffj30rs1jvdy2.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr32ma25ffj30rs1jvdy2-149x300.jpg 149w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr32ma25ffj30rs1jvdy2-509x1024.jpg 509w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>袁、石二位，开始了花样辩解。</p>\n<p>两位老师可算出了口恶气。前几天是大写的尴尬，这当下则是特写的不服。</p>\n<p>笔者有幸，或者不幸，与<b>袁国宝</b>先生在彼此的微信朋友圈。</p>\n<p>与袁先生就此有了交流。</p>\n<p>袁辩解接单者为属下小孩，他的责任仅在失察，他连收了多少钱都不晓得；从年报看伊氏国乳集团是间女子公司，争议重点是其背后公权的滥用。</p>\n<p>我的反驳：接单的是袁先生实名的个人平台，责任推给小孩不适合；并不是伊背后公权的滥用，而是伊在滥用公权，袁老师说反了。</p>\n<p>​<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr3wcyg7fej30u01hcaoc.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-584456\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr3wcyg7fej30u01hcaoc.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr3wcyg7fej30u01hcaoc.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr3wcyg7fej30u01hcaoc-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr3wcyg7fej30u01hcaoc-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>而国宝老师坚持点赞我揶揄大V有偿站台伊利的每一条朋友圈，算是磨砺脸皮？</p>\n<p>如此在意精神修炼的人，人生焉能不成功？</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr3wcxgmhmj30u00qa0zh.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-584455\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr3wcxgmhmj30u00qa0zh.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"394\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr3wcxgmhmj30u00qa0zh.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr3wcxgmhmj30u00qa0zh-300x263.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>​再弱的保险公司都敢一赔一百罢。</p>\n<p>袁师与这魔幻时代的共舞，可以说是如胶似漆、如鱼得水、如痴如醉了。 ​​​​</p>\n<p>袁与石，都祭出了各种金句，以表心计。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr32m8pkm2j30rs1e7n72.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-584460\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr32m8pkm2j30rs1e7n72.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"813\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr32m8pkm2j30rs1e7n72.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr32m8pkm2j30rs1e7n72-166x300.jpg 166w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr32m8pkm2j30rs1e7n72-567x1024.jpg 567w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p><b>一定要想一想自己屁股上有没有没擦干净的屎。——石述思</b><br />\nSave your own ass.<br />\n四川话讲：各人的沟子各人揩哟。</p>\n<p>我将石述思先生的这段话总结为“石述屎”，对此有网友表示不满，认为涉嫌人身攻击。</p>\n<p>鄙人认为：<b>石述思先生阐述揩屎之事，所以石述屎；时传祥同志粪勺不辍，因此时传翔，就事论事，就屎论屎，别无他意。</b><br />\n​<br />\n<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXgy1fr1lyr9lwhj30u0154tmr.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-584451\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXgy1fr1lyr9lwhj30u0154tmr.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"617\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXgy1fr1lyr9lwhj30u0154tmr.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXgy1fr1lyr9lwhj30u0154tmr-219x300.jpg 219w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>大V方阵中的<b>侯宁</b>先生，鄙人通过梳理其公共表现，也算略知一二罢。</p>\n<p>京城核心红二代小心老师曾众筹殴打香港法官。<br />\n​<br />\n<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXgy1fr1lydi09oj30hs0pb4aa.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-584450\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXgy1fr1lydi09oj30hs0pb4aa.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"641\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXgy1fr1lydi09oj30hs0pb4aa.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXgy1fr1lydi09oj30hs0pb4aa-211x300.jpg 211w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>别人随蔡少的份子，都比较谦逊地只跟了一万，侯宁老师一口价十万，傲视群雄。</p>\n<p>所以在这次自媒体红人为伊利集体有偿站台中出现了侯老名字时，不少人不敢相信自己的眼睛。</p>\n<p>不是传说中已经财务自由了么？咋这种卖良心的小钱也赚？</p>\n<p>何况一位知情人士谈到这8点20分集体行动的批发价：</p>\n<p>一点点，少到不好意思说。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr1g2a8ms3j30u00oaqb4.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-584453\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr1g2a8ms3j30u00oaqb4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"364\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr1g2a8ms3j30u00oaqb4.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr1g2a8ms3j30u00oaqb4-300x243.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><br />\n<b>传媒老王</b>？咳咳，咳咳。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr1g2alq48j30u00t4dq0.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-584454\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr1g2alq48j30u00t4dq0.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"437\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr1g2alq48j30u00t4dq0.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr1g2alq48j30u00t4dq0-300x291.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr1g2alq48j30u00t4dq0-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>​您是某药酒销售，跟某记者推销。</p>\n<p>“国际新闻看深度，国内时事读老王，”TA说。</p>\n<p>如果判断对方真心这么认为，恭喜，您可以掏出那瓶比红毛药酒好五倍的了。</p>\n<p>只卖888。</p>\n<p>如果对方其实比猴儿还精，赶紧颠儿，再聊下去您会买下对方代理的药酒。</p>\n<p>只卖8888。</p>\n<p>您可能碰上了正牌的传媒老王。 ​​​ ​​​​</p>\n<p>2018年4月，看了几家公众媒体关于伊利近况的“报道”，大同小异。</p>\n<p>大同嘛，指各家不约而同以报道形式刊发了伊利的公告。</p>\n<p>全文。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr5jr5f2u3j30u01eutr0.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-584458\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr5jr5f2u3j30u01eutr0.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"763\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr5jr5f2u3j30u01eutr0.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr5jr5f2u3j30u01eutr0-177x300.jpg 177w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr5jr5f2u3j30u01eutr0-768x1301.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr5jr5f2u3j30u01eutr0-604x1024.jpg 604w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>这份公告，怎么看怎么像伊利共产党第XX次全体代表大会，领导人潘刚同志发表了热情洋溢的重要讲话。</p>\n<p>利用公共传媒平台的专访证明机构没问题，个人也没事儿，似成惯例，比如2017年新京报专访时任安邦掌门人。</p>\n<p>吴至少还出了台。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr5jwmzuifj30u016eh24.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-584459\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr5jwmzuifj30u016eh24.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"636\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr5jwmzuifj30u016eh24.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr5jwmzuifj30u016eh24-212x300.jpg 212w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr5jwmzuifj30u016eh24-768x1085.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr5jwmzuifj30u016eh24-725x1024.jpg 725w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>现在出一张纸就能给伺候得如此周到，企业的公关压力真是越来越小了。</p>\n<p>嗟，来食！</p>\n<p>仿佛听到了下课铃，同学们夺门而出，冲向了食堂。​</p>\n<p>两大蒙企，一乳一酒，可以说提前锁定2018的年度中国明星企业榜十强了。</p>\n<p>新华社内蒙分社退休记者<b>汤计</b>对呼格错案的执着关注，被认定为后来的改判有过推动，也因此获得庙堂旌表江湖顶礼，是为“义人”。</p>\n<p>要不是学历过高，凭借道德模范优势，如郭明义获封候补中委一般，应该不难。</p>\n<p>同样的执着用于力挺红毛，晓以民族大义，捍卫国产品牌，硬努的姿态想要获得掌声，怕是有些难了。<br />\n​<br />\n<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr59z2wjscj30u01hc4dr.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-584462\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr59z2wjscj30u01hc4dr.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr59z2wjscj30u01hc4dr.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr59z2wjscj30u01hc4dr-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr59z2wjscj30u01hc4dr-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr59z4huegj30u017kk27.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-584463\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr59z4huegj30u017kk27.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"654\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr59z4huegj30u017kk27.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr59z4huegj30u017kk27-207x300.jpg 207w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>汤计老师在中国新闻学院校友群贴出各种为红毛打call的文章，遭遇了讪笑与吐槽，豁达如他，应该不以为忤，也就我这没起子的小校友，觉得有点尴了个尬。</p>\n<p>​<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr5aci9ejgj30nt1o00xf.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-584457\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr5aci9ejgj30nt1o00xf.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"1134\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr5aci9ejgj30nt1o00xf.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr5aci9ejgj30nt1o00xf-119x300.jpg 119w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr5aci9ejgj30nt1o00xf-406x1024.jpg 406w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr59z80sujj30u01hctqa.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-584464\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr59z80sujj30u01hctqa.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr59z80sujj30u01hctqa.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr59z80sujj30u01hctqa-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0072GiCXly1fr59z80sujj30u01hctqa-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><br />\n​<br />\n有网友替汤计老师不平，毕竟蒙古汉子，有偿站台？不可考，人情世故，不可不考。</p>\n<p><b>​智识诚可贵，节操价更高。囿于人情故，二者皆可抛？</b></p>\n<p>经历过八几九几时期商业形态中的官倒儿、拼缝儿，对北京公子哥们的官商勾结能力，应该是刻骨铭心了。</p>\n<p>如今倒是内蒙的官商，传承得有滋有味。</p>\n<p>蒙企中的伊乳鸿酒可谓典范，两手抓两手硬：公安与公关。</p>\n<p>说段见闻：</p>\n<p>2018年3月间，笔者路过公主坟附近裕龙大酒店，停车场有二十余辆警车，以为是首都警方在开会，走近了才看到车牌全“蒙J”, 也就是”药酒圣地“凉城县所在的乌兰察布市。</p>\n<p>首都街头外地公安或法院警车零星常见，但如此成建制啸聚京城，亦为鄙人居京近30年首见。</p>\n<p>草原警方之跨省能力，可以说非常敢上九天揽月敢下五洋捉鳖了。</p>\n<p>正所谓：</p>\n<p><b>草原生意兴隆通四海，公安凛凛威风达三江。</b></p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,9203],"tags":[8635,14716,21038,13826,23678]}